ActsAsFlashcard
===============

ActsAsFlashcard is an adaptation of the Anki ( http://ichi2.net/anki/ ) algorithm for ruby on rails application.

Requirements
============

Rails3 (for Rails2 version please check the corresponding branches)
Has been tested with ruby 1.9.1

Example
=======

class Card < ActiveRecord::Base
  acts_as_flashcard :scope => :user_id
end

card = Card.create
card.answered!(4)

